---
title: Honey Miso Chicken with Ginger Rice & Sesame Sriracha Green Beans
description: Looking for a way to add tons of extra flavor to your meal with almost NO effort? We’ve got two words for you: pan sauce. This one comes together in mere 5 minutes with aromatic scallion and ginger, umami-packed miso sauce concentrate, sweet honey, rich butter, and tangy lime juice. It’s drizzled all over seared chicken cutlets, then served with zesty rice and tender green beans. If you find yourself licking the plate clean, we won’t judge.
